name: Prediction of Bike Rentals
body:
This is a small machine learning side project with the aim of predicting the count of [rental bikes](https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Bike+Sharing+Dataset) with Python. More infos can be found in the IPython notebook. 

#### Acknowledgements

I would like to express my thanks to the [UCI Machine Learning Repository](http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml) for providing the dataset.
